subTitle: Satyam is a budding writer who is always misunderstood by his father. As he struggles to make a mark professionally, his personal life goes through a surprising turn.

subTitle: Jai Simha Reddy, the son of the esteemed Veera Simha Reddy, returns home to avenge his father's death as a result of village politics.

subTitle: Raja, a visually impaired young man, steps in to save Lucky from a gangster's deadly pursuit. Subsequently, touched by his unwavering courage and kindness, Lucky falls in love.

title: Janatha Garage
subTitle: When Anand visits Hyderabad, he encounters Sathyam, who operates an organisation aiding the underprivileged. Sathyam, swayed by Anand's vision, hands over the organisation's management to him.

subTitle: Yashoda agrees to be a surrogate mother to Lucy, an American lady. Unfortunately, during her pregnancy, Yashoda meets with an accident that jeopardises the child's life.

title: Arjun

title: Raju Gari Gadhi
subTitle: Seven young contestants take part in a reality TV show. They spend a week inside a haunted house and soon witness paranormal activities around them.

title: Nene Raju Nene Mantri
subTitle: Driven by his wife's wishes, Jogendra ventures into politics. However, as he climbs the ladder of influence, he risks becoming a heartless power-monger.

title: Nuvve Nuvve

title: Manjummel Boys
subTitle: After one of them falls inside a dangerous pit in the Guna Caves, a group of childhood friends muster courage to rescue him out of a space from where a return is next to impossible.

title: Salaar
subTitle: Just when the prince of Khansaar is about to rise to the throne, a plan of overthrowing him is exercised and only one man can help him retrieve power.

title: The Ghost
subTitle: A former Interpol officer with a troubled past unleashes his skills in an attempt to protect his beloved family from kidnappers, rivals and death.
